  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "The weather that spring stayed mild and sunny, and the tree outside the classroom window grew its first new green leaves.",
      "zh": "那個春天天氣一直很溫和晴朗，教室窗外那棵樹也長出了今年第一批新的綠葉。"
    },
    {
      "en": "In the weeks that followed, Coco noticed small changes she almost missed.",
      "zh": "接下來幾個星期，Coco 注意到一些幾乎沒被發現的小改變。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Wei still checked the vending machine every few days, but now he laughed about it instead of worrying.",
      "zh": "Wei 還是每隔幾天就去看一下那台自動販賣機，但現在他是笑著看，不再擔心了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Mei's name appeared on the practice room list every single week, right at the top.",
      "zh": "Mei 的名字每個星期都出現在練習室名單上，而且都排在最前面。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Locker 113 still had something inside almost every day, though nobody ever agreed on exactly who was doing it.",
      "zh": "113號置物櫃幾乎每天還是有東西，雖然沒有人真正說得清楚是誰在做這件事。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Even Momo the dog became a little famous, with students stopping by at 3:33 just to watch her bark.",
      "zh": "連 Momo 這隻狗都變得有點出名，會有學生特地在三點三十三分過來看她叫。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"We didn't fix the school,\" Bernice said one afternoon. \"We just helped people notice it a little more.\"",
      "zh": "某天下午 Bernice 說：「我們並沒有修好這間學校，我們只是幫大家多注意到它一點。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Maybe that's enough, most of the time,\" Coco said.",
      "zh": "Coco 說：「大多數時候，也許這樣就夠了。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Ms. Ho stopped by the podcast room once, just to say the clock still ran ten minutes slow, exactly as before.",
      "zh": "何老師來過 podcast 教室一次，只是想說那個鐘還是一樣慢十分鐘，跟以前一樣。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Some things,\" she said, \"don't need to change to still matter.\"",
      "zh": "她說：「有些事情，不需要改變，也一樣重要。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Mr. Pan kept teaching English every day, same as always, and never once brought up the Ten Minute Club again.",
      "zh": "潘老師每天還是照常教英文，再也沒有提過十分鐘社的事。"
    },
    {
      "en": "But Coco noticed he always arrived exactly ten minutes before class started, every single morning.",
      "zh": "但 Coco 注意到，他每天早上總是提早十分鐘到教室。"
    },
    {
      "en": "She never asked him why. Some questions, she had learned, were better left as quiet understanding.",
      "zh": "她從來沒問過他為什麼，她學到了，有些問題留著默默懂就好，不用問出口。"
    },
    {
      "en": "As the school year came toward its end, Coco and Bernice sat down to plan their final episode of the year.",
      "zh": "隨著這學年快要結束，Coco 和 Bernice 坐下來計畫這一年的最後一集。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Six cases,\" Bernice said, counting on her fingers. \"No, wait. Seven, if we count our own.\"",
      "zh": "Bernice 一邊數手指一邊說：「六個案子，不對，等等，七個，如果把我們自己也算進去的話。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Coco smiled. \"Maybe that one was always the real one.\"",
      "zh": "Coco 笑了：「也許那一個，才一直是真正的那個案子。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "The school's pet rabbit in the science room grew fat over the winter and needed a bigger cage.",
      "zh": "科學教室裡養的那隻兔子過完冬天變胖了，需要換一個更大的籠子。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A bee got into the classroom one afternoon, and the whole room went a little crazy for five minutes.",
      "zh": "有天下午一隻蜜蜂飛進教室，全班瘋狂了整整五分鐘。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Someone's pet snake escaped during a science project and was found asleep under a bench two days later.",
      "zh": "有人做科展的寵物蛇跑掉了，兩天後才在一張長椅底下找到牠睡著。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A stray cat had kittens behind the gym, and half the school visited them at lunch.",
      "zh": "一隻流浪貓在體育館後面生了小貓，全校一半的人都跑去午餐時間看牠們。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The farmer who sold vegetables near the school gate started bringing ham and cheese to sell too.",
      "zh": "在校門口賣蔬菜的農夫，開始也賣起火腿和起司。"
    },
    {
      "en": "On rainy days, the whole hallway smelled like wet clothes and warm soup from the cafeteria.",
      "zh": "下雨天，整條走廊都聞得到濕衣服和餐廳熱湯的味道。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A new foreign student joined their class in October, and everyone tried to be extra friendly.",
      "zh": "十月時班上來了一位外籍新生，大家都特別努力對他友善。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The school held a small festival in the courtyard, with paper lanterns and a table full of homemade cakes.",
      "zh": "學校在中庭辦了一個小小的園遊會，掛滿紙燈籠，還有一整桌自製蛋糕。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Coco's father, an engineer, came to talk about his job during career week.",
      "zh": "職涯週的時候，Coco 當工程師的爸爸來班上分享他的工作。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice's cousin, a nurse at the city hospital, spoke to their health class about staying healthy.",
      "zh": "Bernice 在市立醫院當護理師的表姊，來健康課跟大家聊怎麼保持健康。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A police officer visited too, along with the owner of the small shop near the market.",
      "zh": "一位警察也來了，還有市場附近那間小商店的老闆。"
    },
    {
      "en": "On the class trip, they saw a giant elephant, a sleepy lion, and two monkeys fighting over a banana at the zoo.",
      "zh": "校外教學時，他們在動物園看到一頭巨大的大象、一隻愛睏的獅子，還有兩隻猴子在搶一根香蕉。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice bought a toy tiger from the gift shop, even though she said she was too old for toys.",
      "zh": "Bernice 在紀念品店買了一隻玩具老虎，雖然她說自己已經太大了不該玩玩具。"
    },
    {
      "en": "On the way home, the bus passed a small farm with cows and sheep resting quietly in the field.",
      "zh": "回程的路上，公車經過一座小農場，牛和羊安靜地在田裡休息。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A bird built a nest above the classroom window, and everyone worried about the baby birds inside.",
      "zh": "一隻鳥在教室窗戶上方築了巢，大家都很擔心裡面的小鳥寶寶。"
    },
    {
      "en": "In science class, they learned how tiny insects like ants and bees help flowers and plants grow.",
      "zh": "在科學課上，他們學到像螞蟻和蜜蜂這樣的小昆蟲，如何幫助花朵和植物生長。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Coco's family celebrated her cousin's wedding that spring; her aunt wore a beautiful new dress and her uncle told the same joke three times.",
      "zh": "那年春天，Coco 一家人參加了表姊的婚禮，阿姨穿了一件漂亮的新洋裝，叔叔把同一個笑話講了三次。"
    },
    {
      "en": "At the wedding, there was a huge dinner with duck, beef, fresh bread, and a giant cake shaped like a heart.",
      "zh": "婚禮上有一頓豐盛的晚餐，有鴨肉、牛肉、新鮮麵包，還有一個心型的大蛋糕。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Every one of these small moments felt separate at the time, Coco thought, but somehow they all belonged to the same busy, ordinary year.",
      "zh": "Coco 覺得，這些小小的時刻在當下都感覺各自獨立，但不知怎麼地，它們全都屬於同一個忙碌又平凡的一年。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Sometimes, during a boring class, Coco would daydream about traveling abroad: a quiet island, a big city with tall towers, or a small town near the sea.",
      "zh": "有時候上課很無聊，Coco 會做白日夢，想像出國旅行：一座安靜的島、一個高樓林立的大城市，或是海邊的一個小鎮。"
    },
    {
      "en": "She imagined taking an airplane to the south, then a taxi from the airport straight to a cheap little hotel by the water.",
      "zh": "她想像搭飛機往南飛，再從機場搭計程車直接到海邊一間便宜的小旅館。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice's daydream was simpler: a national park with a river, a boat, and absolutely no phone reception.",
      "zh": "Bernice 的白日夢比較簡單：一座有河流、有船，而且完全沒有手機訊號的國家公園。"
    }
